<section>
  <h2>📘 Course Overview</h2>
  <p>
    This course provides a comprehensive learning experience covering modern data engineering tools, including 
    <strong>Snowflake, DBT (Data Build Tool), and Azure Data Factory (ADF)</strong>. 
    Designed for real-world application, the course includes hands-on labs, live sessions, and an end-to-end project.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>✨ Course Highlights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Real-time business use case explanations</li>
